# Rule Reputation Ledger

Tracks the effectiveness and trustworthiness of each rule.

---

## Reputation Record Format

- Rule Name:
- Usage Count:
- Impact Score:
- Trustworthiness Score: (computed from usage frequency, failure rate, etc.)
- Last Review Date:
- Last Feedback:
- Feedback Score: (e.g., 1-5 stars)
- Reputation Score: (computed from Trustworthiness and Feedback)

## Reputation Scoring (Example Formula)

- Reputation Score = (Usage Count × Impact Score × Feedback Score) / (Failure Rate + 1)